headline: Q3 Earnings Highs And Lows: Wabtec (NYSE:WAB) Vs The Rest Of The Heavy Transportation Equipment Stocks
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q3. Today, we are looking at heavy transportation equipment stocks, starting with Wabtec (NYSE:WAB).
